{"about_the_game":"Space Wackos is an online and local party shooter for 1-8 players. This low-poly shooter is easy to pickup and go. Inspired by the most popular shooters of the early 2000s, Space Wackos fully embraces casual gameplay and fully local 4-player Split screen for all your party needs.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Local 4-player Split Screen</h2>Space Wackos embraces a lost feature in most modern shooters: Split Screen. It is designed to be playable with no internet and by simply plugging 4 controllers. Evoking the bygone era of couch shooters, Space Wackos is as easy as you can get for a party FPS offering both Coop and PVP that is downloadable in minutes.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Feature-Filled Multiplayer Experience</h2>Online mode offers dozens of armor permutations, a ranking system, a leveling system on over 12 game types and 17 maps. These include many biomes and settings like a remote island, an abandoned temple, a frozen archipelago and a research facility in a swamp. You can also find many remakes of popular maps from one of the most revered shooter ever.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Maxed Out","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2290530/59ffc4c94e49cb8f2a21cb1f2db461977fa6cfc0.jpg"},{"name":"Sir!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2290530/3b323d5c68e672370912a9ab13ac8a3c388d37a8.jpg"},{"name":"Veteran","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2290530/6d74154ee7c6217107fb93f3433f6acb92825bf0.jpg"},{"name":"Sticky Fingers","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2290530/9bf5b52609de19616d9d8dfd97e8c95131c9e4c4.jpg"},{"name":"Martian Hands","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2290530/1de5735c15dbabd88080abf064e53c6697ba9ce5.jpg"},{"name":"You And What Army!?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2290530/c18ebd24ef